    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>20 Upper Woburn <sic>place</sic> Favistock Sq.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>London</placeName>
                <date>March 13<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1857</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Some time since I received the <sic>inclosed</sic><lb/> note from
                    <persName>Mr Rintel</persName> of <placeName>Melbourne</placeName> which I now
                beg<lb/> to forward you together with the sum of Three pounds<lb/> ten shillings and
                beg you will acknowledge the<lb/> receipt of same to <persName>Mr. Rintel</persName>
                at your earliest<lb/> convenience, as his note will fully inform you of<lb/> the
                state of the Australian market for Jewish publication<lb/> I need not make any
                further remarks thereon.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I proceed to <placeName>Melbourne</placeName> together with
                    <persName>Mrs Hart</persName> and<lb/> children on the <date>16<hi rend="sup"
                        >th</hi></date> Proximo, and if my services can be<lb/> of any benefit I
                shall be pleased to serve you, during<lb/> my short stay there, when any
                communication ad=<lb/>=dressed to the care of <persName>Messrs de Beer, Moser &amp;
                    Co. Merchant</persName><lb/>
                <placeName>Bourk St Melbourne</placeName> will meet me. And with best<lb/> wishes
                believe me</p>
            <p rend="indent(8)">Yours Very Truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">
                <persName role="author">Henri J Hart</persName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd. I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
